Scope of this license
---------------------
Apache-2.0 covers the AusMT FRAMEWORK in this repository — the offline build
engine (engine/), the static portal (portal/), documentation (docs/), the
maintainer knowledge base (maintainer/), and tooling.

It does NOT cover the magnetotelluric survey DATA that AusMT processes, indexes,
and serves — transfer functions and survey metadata. That data is licensed
individually by its custodians (typically CC-BY-4.0) and is maintained in the
separate `ausmt-surveys` repository. The sample survey bundled under
`engine/data/` for testing carries its own LICENSE.md (CC-BY-4.0).
